As part of Avon's Major Global Initiatives Project, we have invested significant portions of the Project's capital to improving Associate safety and property protection.  At our Zanesville facility, capital went directly into the design and construction of the facility, which includes the Aerosol Product Flammable Mixture Storage Area.  This area was designed and built with the following attributes:
