Avon's commitment to safety continues with our material handling policies.  These policies are in place as an administrative step to prevention.  These policies include the Handling & Storage of Aerosol Products Policy.  Components of this policy include, but are not limited to:
Â¿Move unloaded aerosol pallet loads to the Warehouse Aerosol Room immediately and avoid temporary storage in the Receiving dock area;
Â¿Once an aerosol pallet has been delivered to the Warehouse Aerosol Room remove or cut the plastic off the top of the pallet to allow water penetration through the pallet in the event of a fire;
Â¿Use only EE rated forklifts or manual power jacks to transport aerosol pallet loads;
Â¿In production areas only store the aerosol products required for one-shift;
Â¿Designate areas for holding aerosol products in production areas;
