hen not in the Warehouse Aerosol Room;
Â¿Do not place aerosol loads in or near aisle intersections or in heavy traffic areas; 
Â¿Flammable or combustible liquids will not be stored within 2.4m (8 ft) of aerosols;
Â¿Do not locate high hazard operations (i.e. battery charging) within 8m (25 ft) of the Warehouse Aerosol Room;
