THE FACILITY AND THE REGULATED SUBSTANCES STORED
Avon's Zanesville facility stores and handles health and beauty consumer products, some of which are packaged in aerosol containers.  These aerosol containers may have a flammable mixture of chemical with propane and isobutene, used as propellants.  Avon may store up to a total 14,257 pounds of the flammable mixtures.  
For purposes of this plan, our worst case release scenario would occur outside of the Aerosol Product Flammable Mixture Storage Area, although the subject products are handled in accordance with the Handling & Storage of Aerosol Products Policy and are stored in the specially designed, constructed, and maintained Aerosol Product Flammable Mixture Storage Area.  

